{"tid":977719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓋版廣告玩完了！Google 正式宣佈 Chrome 廣告阻擋政策今年適用全球","createTime":"2019-01-11T11:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T13:47:17.000Z","uid":153228,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c391e7fcecd5de870665f44d5d6790880c293d67","tid":977719,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:36:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/article/15260-chrome-ad-standards\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside.com.tw%2Farticle%2F15260-chrome-ad-standards&d=Xh0JtrJl6J7LPQciRdIjxlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=13e20302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inside.com.tw/article/15260-chrome-ad-standards</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://inside-assets1.inside.com.tw/2019/1/9c17t0evrf2crq730e5k795j16c4zk.png?auto=compress&amp;fit=max&amp;w=730\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finside-assets1.inside.com.tw%2F2019%2F1%2F9c17t0evrf2crq730e5k795j16c4zk.png%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26fit%3Dmax%26w%3D730&h=f9964de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 今日也正式在官方部落格表示，追隨廣告聯盟（Coalition for Better Ads）今年一月宣布全球適用的桌機與行動設備的違規廣告標準， Chrome 廣告阻擋也將從 2019年7月 9 日推往全球市場。<br />\n<br />\n蓋版、彈出式甚至是影音廣告降低用戶體驗，身為瀏覽器巨頭的 Google 在加入廣告聯盟（Coalition for Better Ads）後，也與聯盟夥伴開始正視這些廣告問題。繼去年 Google 下達通令在 Chrome 新的廣告政策，不論是行動裝置或 PC上，只要是蓋板廣告、跳出式影片等廣告等都會被瀏覽器阻擋並遭到除權，這項公告在當時震驚不少出版商與廣告商。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，在去年新政策已於歐洲與北美的網站開始實行，除了阻擋這些傷害用戶體驗的違規廣告，Google 自家的廣告平台也停止銷售此類違反標準的廣告類型，並開放 Chrome 用戶可對此進行投訴，在今年上述標準將不限於歐美適用所有國家。<br />\n<br />\n蓋版、彈跳、自動播放音樂 到底哪些算違規？<br />\n<br />\nGoogle 說明在規範中共有 12 大類，如下圖所示的廣告類型，是根據廣告聯盟調查全球 66,000 位用戶針對廣告體驗得到的回饋所歸類出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://inside-assets2.inside.com.tw/2019/1/rifpasi9pakhg0a4bb2gkjr3k3wu5p.png?auto=compress&amp;fit=max&amp;w=730\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finside-assets2.inside.com.tw%2F2019%2F1%2Frifpasi9pakhg0a4bb2gkjr3k3wu5p.png%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26fit%3Dmax%26w%3D730&h=a76d9259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身自己也是廣告商的 Google 也特別強調，阻擋廣告的目的並非要扼殺廣告市場，積極來說除了將用戶體驗優先，另一方面也在鼓勵廣告商能用更有效益的方式重新設計廣告，而這樣的方式初步在歐美市場實行的結果也相當不錯，據統計在新政策上路時有高達三分之一的廠商都不合規，經過調整截至今年1月1日，Google 審核數百萬網站裡僅有有不到 1％ 的網站上有廣告遭到阻擋。<br />\n<br />\n過去對廣告商來說，流量轉換大過於用戶體驗，讓使用者相當頭痛，只能仰賴 Ad Block 來維持清爽的瀏覽過程，這次新政策對網路圈來說是一項大變革，在用戶們拍手叫好不用再依靠 Ad Block 時，廣告商們也被逼著思考如何將用戶體驗優先符合規範標準，開始著手下一步的廣告轉型。<br />\n<br />\n詳細標準可見規範<a href=\"https://www.betterads.org/standards/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.betterads.org%2Fstandards%2F&d=Xh0JtrJl6J7LPQciRdIjxlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=4c8e9657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.betterads.org/standards/</a>"},{"pid":"4906d02da63e958547bc5f5c24ce2fe280743530","tid":977719,"uid":82359,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"咁YouTube 啲死人廣告幾時又block 埋佢？"},{"pid":"cb70b3bf10587d78b60d6e538f493192e3cbebe4","tid":977719,"uid":61524,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"4906d02da63e958547bc5f5c24ce2fe280743530","tid":977719,"uid":82359,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:44:20.000Z","msg":"咁YouTube 啲死人廣告幾時又block 埋佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"真係好撚煩，睇一條片彈3，4次廣告，有時重要係啲19youtuber 廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de647ea6f0f7746eb537096c98d06c2b677a5341","tid":977719,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:00:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"439edfa538487dfc1126132c145099e4248c3b53","tid":977719,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"上線了！"},{"pid":"12d1398b4ec65d5bdf333d97f4d308f714da57b5","tid":977719,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"雖然係好事<br />\n不過你啲濕鳩Youtube廣告呢?"},{"pid":"d807086550e75af48ec4159c4f646025e322a0e5","tid":977719,"uid":15477,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"